data.description: Get out of the COLD come south, NOW!  Affordable Nice, Comfortable Home in nice quiet area, with property owners association. 1766 Sq.ft Concrete Block Stucco home. 3bd. 2bth, Split Bedroom Floor Plan. Living Room , Combined Dining/Kitchen, Separates Master Bedroom from other 2 Bedrooms. Screen porch to enjoy nice fenced back yard.  2 Car Garage plus concrete driveway accommodates more. Nicely landscaped 98 X 142 lot approx. 13,916 sq. ft lot.  Pool & Club House amenities for when the family and friends come they can get out of your house and enjoy. No neighbor to the right. Nor directly behind. Walking trail or golf cart trails lead towards lake.  No hustle bustle here. For those who are seeking relaxation and sunshine! 3 doors to outside from house Central A/C wih heat, Gable Hip Roof,  Jet Tub, Walk in Closet, stove, fridge, microwave, washer, dryer, dishwasher. Tile floors except for bedrooms are carpet.  Peace & Quiet is what you'll find here. Please call to see. Property Owners Association $25.month. then $150 a year for sprinkler system. Don't end up in a bad neighborhood buy this one! 3 % Realtor compensation being offered. Sign on Property! No trespassing. Easy to Show. Call to get in and see.
data.whatILove: Well maintained. Looking for true Florida Living,  then this house is a must see. Home is over 1700 sqft of living space with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Large Master bedroom and over sized bathroom with walk-in shower and jacuzzi tub.  Kitchen and family room open to each other providing a great place for family and/or entertaining. Home is located in a quiet neighborhood and is also close to schools, hospitals, shopping and minutes from public access lakes for fishing, swimming & boating.  Ceiling fans, tile floors,  attic ladder in the garage for attic access, electric garage door opener, high ceiling,  screened in patio with sliding glass doors overlooking your newly landscaped with new wood privacy fence  in back yard. Call for showing 863 452- 2892.
